It's a simply shell to install hadoop on CentOS 5.X which can made 
hadoop installation easier and faster.

The hadoop installed with this script would be a fake distributed,
but you can comment some lines to use it with real distributed 
network.

It support lzo compressed data file by default, so enjoy it.

Usage:
[root@yourhost]#chmod +x EasyHadoop.sh
[root@yourhost]#EasyHadoop.sh 6 2 512

The arguments means: 6(max map tasks) 2(max reduce tasks) 512(max java memory usage)